     H            Y.
     F** AB#RBJ *************************************************************
     F*  VALIDATE UNSCANNED LABEL (EXTERNAL)                                *
     F*                                                                     *
     F*  JW   09/23/2016                                                    *
     F*----------------------------------------------------------------------
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'AB#RBJ'
     F*                    PARM           $NONY   4
     F*                    PARM           $NKOJ   1
     F*                    PARM           $NUKE   4
     F*                    PARM           $SHIN  12
     F*                    PARM           $NOHZ   8
     F*                    PARM           $NOBN   2
     F*                    PARM           $ORDN  10
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*   IN  $NONY   4A DELIVERY#
     F*       $NKOJ   1A FACTORY
     F*       $NUKE   4A DOCK
     F*       $SHIN  12A IAF PART1
     F*       $NOHZ   8A SHIP DATE
     F*       $NOBN   2A BIN
     F*       $ORDN  10A ORDER#
     F*   OUT $RTN    1A RETURN FLAG (Y:RECORD EXISTS, N:NOT)
     F*****************************************************************
     FAB#WL0G IF  E           K        DISK
      *----------------------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1  12 WSHIN
     I                                        1   5 $SHN1
     I                                        6  10 $SHN2
     I                                       11  12 $SHN3
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      *---------------------------------------------------------
      *  MAIN
      *---------------------------------------------------------
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $NONY   4
     C                     PARM           $NKOJ   1
     C                     PARM           $NUKE   4
     C                     PARM           $SHIN  12
     C                     PARM           $NOHZ   8
     C                     PARM           $NOBN   2
     C                     PARM           $ORDN  10
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *
     C           KEY       KLIST
     C                     KFLD           @NONY
     C                     KFLD           $NKOJ
     C                     KFLD           $NUKE
     C                     KFLD           $SHN1
     C                     KFLD           $SHN2
     C                     KFLD           $SHN3
     C                     KFLD           @NOHZ
     C                     KFLD           @NOBN
     C                     KFLD           $ORDN
      *
     C                     MOVE 'N'       $RTN
     C                     MOVEL$SHIN     WSHIN
     C                     MOVEL$NONY     @NONY   40
     C                     MOVEL$NOHZ     @NOHZ   80
     C                     MOVEL$NOBN     @NOBN   20
      *
     C           KEY       CHAINAB#WL0G              99
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       $RTN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
